  "instructions": [
    "Crush the digestive biscuits into fine crumbs and set aside.",
    "Wash and dry the baby spinach leaves.",
    "Thinly slice the cucumber and tomato into sashimi‑style strips.",
    "Place the spinach, cucumber, and tomato in a large bowl.",
    "Add the chopped mint and cilantro to the bowl.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil and lemon juice over the vegetables.",
    "Sprinkle the ground cumin, salt, and pepper, then toss gently to combine.",
    "Add the crumbled biscuits to the salad and toss again until evenly distributed.",
    "Serve immediately for a fresh crunch, or chill for 15 minutes for a slightly firmer bite."
